    {
      "id": "PopularPost309582",
      "post_content": "Note that if your opponent has more life than you this lets you murder all their planeswalkers. Additionally, if you're running {R}/{W} and using cards like [Worship](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Worship), [Fortune Thief](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fortune Thief), [Angel's Grace](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Angel's Grace), and others to stabilize at low life totals, this can be a win condition all by itself. Being instant means you can use your mana to defend yourself if necessary, perhaps with Fateful Hour cards?",
      "posted_by": "LordRandomness",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost309582\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Note that if your opponent has more life than you this lets you murder all their planeswalkers. Additionally, if you're running {R}/{W} and using cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Worship\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Worship\">Worship</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fortune Thief\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fortune Thief\">Fortune Thief</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Angel's Grace\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Angel's Grace\">Angel's Grace</a>, and others to stabilize at low life totals, this can be a win condition all by itself. Being instant means you can use your mana to defend yourself if necessary, perhaps with Fateful Hour cards?</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '309582'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy76236\">LordRandomness</span>\r\n                                (5/22/2013 12:50:43 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"